ro:Statuia lui Vasile Alecsandri din Iași

The museum is organized in the house where the poet lived and wrote between 1934 and 1957 (the "Sonet Villa"). The exhibition rooms belonged after the poet's death to his wife who left them in her will for a memorial exhibition. Three of the rooms - the

Muzeul este organizat in casa in care a locuit si a scris poetul, in perioada 1934 - 1957 ("Vila Sonet"). Camerele amenajate expozitional au apartinut, dupa moartea poetului, sotiei acestuia, care le-a lasat prin testament in vederea amenajarii expozitie
